The title "Actual Life Vol. 1" comes from one of my favorite music producers Fred again.. 

His music samples youtube videos and tik-toks and friends voicemails. His samples' sheer rawness, yet mundaneness, show the romance we can find in life if we take the time to look around.

More than ever today we are so caught up on looking ahead or looking down. That we forget to take in the views all around. This collection comes from those moments of looking around. https://t.co/jOCsFDJfvU

Photography is not my main medium of creation. However, just like all the other facets of my life. I love the rawness and beauty of mundane life. 

This collection reflects the beauty we can find in our mundane lives as long as we take the time to look around. https://t.co/XkxUDrGCh6
